data.description: This beautiful and spacious one-story home is on an oversize lot, Cul-de-sac in Orange Branch Bay Gated Community. It offers 4 bedrooms with 3 full baths, 3 car garages and has an open layout. There are ceramic titles on the living areas and laminated wood floors in all the bedrooms. As you enter you will find on your left the spacious living room/dining room combination and on your right, you can find two spacious bedrooms and a bathroom with the laundry room right across. Further in through the hallway you enter a big/spacious family room and kitchen combination with an island including granite countertops. On the left you will find bedroom #3 with a bathroom just next door. The Master bedroom on the right is spacious with enough room for a king size bed and a seating area, open the door to your spa-like bathroom with a walk-in closet. 2016 Roof, with a Windmit already done for your convenience, 2023 A/C and more. The back yard is amazing with a large screen covered porch and a huge backyard. 12 months, home buyer warranty included with this home.
